name: Cool Pet #1300
description:
I wonder what's inside?

An NFT offering from the Cool Cats brand, Cool Pets is a collection of 19,999 NFTs that are procedurally generated based on item interaction. All Cool Pets start as an Egg and evolve into their final form, which represents one of four elements: Grass, Fire, Water, or Air.

Users can evolve their Cool Pet through our gamified experience on [www.coolcatsnft.com](https://www.coolcatsnft.com/) – your final Cool Pet is one of 17 million possible outcomes! To learn more about Cool Pets, Eggs, and the world of Cooltopia, visit [cooltopia.coolcatsnft.com](https://cooltopia.coolcatsnft.com/). We love the Pets!
